  ¬∑ intro param k R v hkR hv; simpa using hRel param k R v hkR hv
  ¬∑ intro param k R v hkR hv; simpa using hNRel param k R v hkR hv
  ¬∑ intro param; simpa using hverum param
  ¬∑ intro param; simpa using hfalsum param
